column6: - We the people find you DOOM! - When the son of Victor Von Doom seeks extradition, Jen Walters will go to the ends of the earth for Justice! - All this, and Matt Murdock too as Charles Soule (THUNDERBOLTS) and Javier Pulido (HAWKEYE) continue 2014's sleeper hit!
column8: | artist:Javier Pulido | writer:Charles Soule | penciller (cover):Kevin P. Wada
